{"tid":2199572,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[熱氣師] 鹹蛋黃炸雞","createTime":"2020-09-12T10:03:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-14T13:18:52.000Z","uid":113525,"like":95,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"5f2dd564679e2b78d1703e5b8bd9655a3659fe96","tid":2199572,"uid":113525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T10:03:24.000Z","msg":"早幾日係街食左個鹹蛋黃炸雞 覺得幾好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以就自己試下整<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n製成品<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/onrUzmC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FonrUzmC.jpg&h=512f8148&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n鹹蛋黃 隔水蒸6分鐘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0d7wBAa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0d7wBAa.jpg&h=c86db8a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雞扒勿走多餘既皮同埋肥膏，之後切塊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/srU69VC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsrU69VC.jpg&h=4fa313ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一個盤有麵粉、紅椒粉、蒜鹽同埋黑胡椒，係炸粉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另一個盤有雞蛋、水、麵粉、鹽同埋黑胡椒，係炸漿 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n分別撈勻<br />\n之後先上炸漿，再上炸粉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vAi7Uod.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvAi7Uod.jpg&h=1be4a13b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n落油中火炸大約兩分鐘，夾起攤凍少少，之後再轉大火炸至金黃色同埋脆身 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C8TDgBX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC8TDgBX.jpg&h=296c8f55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kTM9ohb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkTM9ohb.jpg&h=f71a45fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n煎pan加牛油同埋鹹蛋黃，壓碎蛋黃 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/msKbBCt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmsKbBCt.jpg&h=75a410d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n加熱至起泡，加入炸雞炒幾下，就食得喇! <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kHARBCN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkHARBCN.png&h=c61bed3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n食評: 炸雞炸左兩次好脆，但又唔會乾，加埋鹹蛋黃味，送啤酒真係一流 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n          食落個喉嚨好熱氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有興趣既可以睇下條片同埋記得訂閱我呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PInlMMvukx4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPInlMMvukx4&d=D4HIriwr0d5ovb2eA4y9f3jCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=0f0b2641\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PInlMMvukx4</a><br />\n<br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/%E9%A3%9F%E5%8B%BB%E5%85%A8%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C-Eating-around-the-World-104348851320921/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%25E9%25A3%259F%25E5%258B%25BB%25E5%2585%25A8%25E4%25B8%2596%25E7%2595%258C-Eating-around-the-World-104348851320921%2F&d=D4HIriwr0d5ovb2eA4y9f3jCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=d699a1aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/%E9%A3%9F%E5%8B%BB%E5%85%A8%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C-Eating-around-the-World-104348851320921/</a><br />\n<br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/eatingaroundthe_World/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Featingaroundthe_World%2F&d=D4HIriwr0d5ovb2eA4y9f3jCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=de323683\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/eatingaroundthe_World/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n共業 REDSTOP 網頁版出世啦<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2198432\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2198432</a>"},{"pid":"8fd1a0ae011e7363a3ce195bce361007fa832081","tid":2199572,"uid":33359,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T10:04:46.000Z","msg":"再點D羅勒香蒜醬會更好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57da0c917392ff88979a0a014b0b5738473b55b1","tid":2199572,"uid":113525,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8fd1a0ae011e7363a3ce195bce361007fa832081","tid":2199572,"uid":33359,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T10:04:46.000Z","msg":"再點D羅勒香蒜醬會更好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T10:05:48.000Z","msg":"你仲好講 問你係邊度買又唔答我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"500aab9b19fcffb89108f31a6bea2b413aa6677b","tid":2199572,"uid":113525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T10:12:50.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6cbb51e64ec53cdc53d4b98265d9496b89b1ffe1","tid":2199572,"uid":33359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"57da0c917392ff88979a0a014b0b5738473b55b1","tid":2199572,"uid":113525,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8fd1a0ae011e7363a3ce195bce361007fa832081","tid":2199572,"uid":33359,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T10:04:46.000Z","msg":"再點D羅勒香蒜醬會更好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T10:05:48.000Z","msg":"你仲好講 問你係邊度買又唔答我<img src=\"/assets/faces/